          {
            "_key": "b7320c8c-66f7-4054-8b65-b471831a33ab",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "取得しておくと役立つ研修"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "0d118c60-e631-40a6-ba73-543c4f45a06b",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "912481a2-4939-4727-b8d8-355190c7d7b7",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "介護職員初任者研修：身体介助や感染対策の基礎を体系的に学べます。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "33be7600-e97c-4949-afba-843e1a4ff2a5",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "cdd21893-625c-46ff-b393-652cbbe3f211",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "実務者研修：より高度な介助や記録の書き方を学び、リーダー補佐として活躍しやすくなります。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "3f7a784a-00af-4a47-8721-261bdfea095e",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "a73eb742-5f78-4e7f-9f21-ea95162c10de",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "介護福祉士：国家資格として信頼性が高く、将来のキャリアアップにもつながります。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "section-closing-15d3942c-abb2-4419-b9eb-cfb0e64d79f4",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "section-closing-span-0cf2f052-3487-4cc8-81bb-e4e874525505",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "取得しておくと役立つ研修では、看護師と連携しながら無理のない範囲で進めることが大切です。気になる点はその都度共有し、安全第一で取り組みましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "c4341bfc-f143-4c0e-8ce0-f4a1d185e609",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "11279d41-c008-474a-9651-7d4bd4cde23a",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "未経験で働く前に準備したいこと"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "63a5bf89-212c-4822-b669-ca70aac80a27",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "9584d443-22e6-49cf-a352-8871fe8e4c98",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "体力づくり：簡単なストレッチや筋力トレーニングを習慣にしておくと、初めての夜勤でもスムーズです。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "eee9181f-c61e-4f93-9c2c-e3edc832aa87",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "ab7d7735-842d-464c-a9cf-015be98a7d86",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "生活リズムの調整：夜勤や早番がある職場では、睡眠や食事の時間を事前に調整しておくと体調管理がしやすくなります。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "f8c73f3e-0d0f-4fea-9a48-39dd9e158768",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "463fb5be-8b8a-4cb8-9b1c-a3ebc1b499a1",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "情報収集：病院・施設ごとの研修制度やサポート体制を調べ、自分が安心できる環境かを確認しましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "followup-03531da9-df57-414e-a746-842d01ab8d40",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "text-7152817c-7657-4227-90e1-aafeba152ffd",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "上記の点に注意しながら、無理なく取り組んでいきましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
